1982 — NEC V20 8080 Emulation Mode

Mostly compatible extension of the Intel 8086, with added Intel 8080 emulation. The following table lists the instructions in the 8080 Emulation Mode.

Address space
20-bit
Emulation address space
16-bit
I/O space
16-bit
Operation modes
Native mode (8086 compatible) vs emulation mode (8080 compatible)

Main table

  • Green marks new instructions to the Intel 8080.
  • Red marks new instructions replacing earlier ones for the Intel 8080.
  • Orange marks instructions present but undocumented in Intel 8080 and documented for the NEC V20.
  • Pink background marks undocumented instructions.
  • Plum background marks duplicate instructions.
